Author: Satrajit Ghosh <satrajitghosh183@gmail.com>
Date:   Fri Dec 5 14:38:01 2025 -0500

    Major game engine overhaul - Professional studio-quality tower defense
    
    NEW FILES:
    - EnemyManager.js: Sophisticated wave spawning with formations (line, V, swarm, pincer)
    - GraphicsEngine.js: PBR rendering, 4 themes (hellfire/frost/nature/void), bloom, vignette shaders
    - TowerCombatSystem.js: Advanced targeting AI (8 modes), 7 projectile types, chain lightning
    
    REWRITES:
    - Enemy.js: 20+ enemy types with abilities (phasing, teleport, rage, shields, healing aura)
    - EnemyTypes.js: 4-tier enemy system with unique behaviors and visual configs
    - EnhancedGame.js: Integrated all new systems, professional base with animated crystal
    - Game1v1.js: Full multiplayer with income system, wave sending, territory control
    - Tower.js: Turret aiming, 3-level upgrades, targeting modes, range indicators
    
    FEATURES:
    - Proper enemy spawning with wave templates (tutorial, boss, swarm, elite)
    - Difficulty scaling: easy/normal/hard/nightmare presets
    - Quality presets: low/medium/high/ultra graphics
    - Enemy abilities: shields, splitting, healing, EMP, berserker rage
    - Tower projectiles: homing missiles, instant lasers, chain tesla
    - Post-processing: bloom, SMAA, custom damage vignette shader

